attributes.title: HORRIBLE
attributes.review: UGH HORRIBLE HORRIBLE APP!!! I IMMEDIATELY OPENED THE APP AND SAW A DISGUSTING ORANGE CRUSTY LOOKING MAN AND IT TRIGGERED MY GAG REFLEX! I COULD NOT STOP VOMITING FOR HOURS. THEN AS I CONTINUED TO USE THE APP IT SHOWED ITS TRUE COLORS; HORRIBLE QUALITY, TERRIBLE APP! ⚠️DO NOT DOWNLOAD⚠️
